<Link id="l00045" /><CodeLine lineNumber="45"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// operand in place of the immediate Value in the MCInst.  The immediate</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00046" /><CodeLine lineNumber="46"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Value has not had any PC adjustment made by the caller. If the instruction</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00047" /><CodeLine lineNumber="47"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// is a branch that adds the PC to the immediate Value then isBranch is</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00048" /><CodeLine lineNumber="48"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Success, else Fail. If GetOpInfo is non-null, then it is called to get any</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00049" /><CodeLine lineNumber="49"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// symbolic information at the Address for this instrution.  If that returns</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00050" /><CodeLine lineNumber="50"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// non-zero then the symbolic information it returns is used to create an</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00051" /><CodeLine lineNumber="51"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// MCExpr and that is added as an operand to the MCInst.  If GetOpInfo()</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00052" /><CodeLine lineNumber="52"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// returns zero and isBranch is Success then a symbol look up for</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00053" /><CodeLine lineNumber="53"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Address + Value is done and if a symbol is found an MCExpr is created with</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00054" /><CodeLine lineNumber="54"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// that, else an MCExpr with Address + Value is created.  If GetOpInfo()</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00055" /><CodeLine lineNumber="55"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// returns zero and isBranch is Fail then the Opcode of the MCInst is</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00056" /><CodeLine lineNumber="56"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// tested and for ADRP an other instructions that help to load of pointers</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00057" /><CodeLine lineNumber="57"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// a symbol look up is done to see it is returns a specific reference type</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00058" /><CodeLine lineNumber="58"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// to add to the comment stream.  This function returns Success if it adds</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00059" /><CodeLine lineNumber="59"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// an operand to the MCInst and Fail otherwise.</span></CodeLine>
